$interpreted: Maria: Chu Chu, look~ It's your partner!
Chu Chu: Choo~choo~choo~choo~choo
Maria: Is Chu Chu hungry? Master Clark said Maria can't eat, but Chu Chu can.
Wussy Sailor: Mr. Waits, that's her!
Buff Sailor: We've been watching them two for some days now.
Buff Sailor: That fella's come from the Rune Academy. I asked around and heard he's headed towards the Mechanical Territory via ferry.
Mr. Waits: ...Mechanical Territory, eh?
Wussy Sailor: Look! She can even fly!
Rune Sorcerer: Wah? I've never seen this type of Rune activation...
Mr. Waits: This robot is a masterpiece. I must have her!
Maria: Chu Chu wants to eat Maria's hair? Master says you can't eat hair~
Maria: Eh? Chu Chu, where are you going? Wait for Maria!
Clark: Maria, Chu Chu won't fly far. Don't you go running off now.
Brown Noser: Has the ferry to the MT been arranged for Mr. Waits?
Rough Fella: Of course. When's da boss headin' out?
Brown Noser: About two, three days. We're ready whenever!
Rough Fella: Got it! We'd best find ourselves some more helpers, ya hear!?
Maria: Hey, Chu Chu!
Mr. Waits: Is this your little birdie? Here you go.
Maria: Master Clark told me that in this situation I should say thank you. Thank you!
Mr. Waits: Do you like the little bird?
Maria: Yes! Little birds are fun. They can fly with me. They also have many friends~
Mr. Waits: I have a bald eagle at my house. Would you like to play with it?
Maria: Maria's never seen a bird that big before!
Mr. Waits: Well, bald eagles are a rare species! Of course you've never seen one. Come on! Your new friend will take you there to see him!
Maria: Master Clark said I can't go running off now.
Mr. Waits: Master? You don't even know where your own master is.
Maria: Master Clark? Master Clark?
Mr. Waits: Forget about him, come home with me! I'll buy you as many birds as you want!
Maria: No, no! Maria wants to go find her master!
Maria: Give me back Chu...NO!
Maria: Chu...Chu...
Mr. Waits: You broke her! Didn't I tell you not to hurt her!
Rune Sorcerer: ...It seems that it is merely in sleep mode. Let's bring her back immediately.
Clark: Strange. I definitely just heard him say there was a ferry to the Mechanical Territory...
Clark: Eh? Maria?
Clark: Maria? Maria?
Clark: Is this...?
